## ⚔️ How Battles Work

- **Three Formations** – you must prepare **three distinct hero + troop squads**.  
  - In the **Qualifier** you fight all rounds with those same three teams.  
  - From **Elimination** onward, each Best‑of‑3 match uses one formation per round. First to win **two rounds** advances.
- **Zero Troop Loss** – all battles are simulated. You can safely use your highest‑tier troops every fight.
- **Lockdown Rule** – lineups are frozen 1 minute before each battle. No last‑second switches.

